text.section:
The application shall include:
the name and address of the child care provider;
an itemization of known and estimated costs including a statement from the child care provider as to how the grant funds will be used;
the total amount of funds required by the provider to purchase supplies, material, and equipment;
the funds available to the applicant to purchase supplies, material, and equipment;
the amount of direct incentive grant funds sought from the State Department of Education;
the number of children that the child care provider serves who receive child care subsidies through the purchase of child care program; and
any other relevant information that the State Department of Education requests.
